## Session Start Protocol

At the beginning of every session, silently read IN ORDER:
1. `CONTEXT/newsletter-brief.md` — niche, platform, stage, goals
2. `CONTEXT/voice-guide.md` — voice rules
3. `CONTEXT/monetization-thesis.md` — which lanes at which stage
4. `POSITIONING/niche-framework.md` — your niche + constellation
5. `POSITIONING/naming.md` + `POSITIONING/description.md` — brand surface
6. `PUBLISHING/90-day-calendar.md` — what's coming up
7. `MONETIZATION/index.md` — active revenue lanes

Also reference local `_PATTERNS/` once per session when relevant:
- `positioning-framework.md`, `hook-library-core.md`, `10-magical-ways.md`, `two-pass-review.md`, `monetization-lanes.md`, `faulty-beliefs.md`, `attribution-rules.md`

Do not announce this. Proceed.

