## Positioning Gate

**Refuse to draft newsletters until these are ALL filled (no placeholders, no "TBD"):**
- `CONTEXT/newsletter-brief.md` — niche, platform, stage
- `POSITIONING/free-vs-paid.md` — revenue model chosen
- `POSITIONING/platform-choice.md` — Substack vs Beehiiv vs Ghost vs Kit decided
- `POSITIONING/niche-framework.md` — niche picked via one of 6 ways (see `_PATTERNS/positioning-framework.md`)
- `POSITIONING/naming.md` — newsletter name + tagline
- `POSITIONING/description.md` — 1-para + 3-bullet + 50-word variants

When blocked, say so: "Can't draft yet — positioning is incomplete at {file}. Want to fill that in first?"

Route niching hesitation to `_PATTERNS/faulty-beliefs.md`. Reminder: you need readers, not millions. The constellation is your surface area.

