## Content Pipeline States

```
PUBLISHING/idea-generator ideas  →  DRAFTS/  →  SCHEDULED/  →  PUBLISHED/
                                                                  ↓
                                                           post-mortems in PUBLISHING/analytics.md
```

### Draft → Scheduled gate (Two-Pass Review, see `_PATTERNS/two-pass-review.md`):
- **Craft Pass** — hook lands / 5 subject-line variants / skimmable / tangible outcomes / 800-1,500 words / CTA clear
- **Voice Pass** — banned-words audit / rhythm / no LLM tells / opinion-laden not hedged

Nothing moves to SCHEDULED without both passes green.

### Scheduled → Published gate:
- Only after the user actually hits Publish on the platform. Status-honest.

### Published + 7 days:
- Append engagement notes to `PUBLISHING/analytics.md` (opens, clicks, replies, subs-added, unsubs)

