First Monday of month: Cascade surfaces "Time for the monthly mirror drill. Pick 3 newsletters you opened + read fully this month. Let's deconstruct them via `PROMPTS/generators/mirror-prompt.md` (or link to creator-studio's version)."

Log findings in `PUBLISHING/mirror-ritual.md`.

